{"title":"孩子的诗","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":12,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子的诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一栏里选的是河北怀来县果林公社孩子们的诗。果林公社是花果之乡，也是诗歌之乡。果林公社的社员，都能歌善诗。孩子们也成了诗歌能手。他们一边念书一边劳动，写下了不少的诗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小作者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别看作者小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗歌可不少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心超过杜甫诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快马加鞭赶郭老。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（工农中学一年级"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘玉花）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多亏咱们毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕地用上拖拉机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村里安上电话机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"食堂用上吹风机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家里安上收音机。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要问这些哪里来？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多亏咱们毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（小矾山小学五年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"级靳永根）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大丰收"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社里今年大丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食堆的顶住天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳差点过不去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞机只得绕个弯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（果林学校一年级"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张进生）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈赞食堂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花喜鹊，喳喳叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈天天面带笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她笑啥？我知道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社成立幸福到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下地回来进食堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再忙着把饭烧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（工农中学一年级"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛洪邦）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也够太阳晒几天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社社员千千万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人多力大胜过天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每人流下一滴汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也够太阳晒几天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二堡小学五年级"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"段有）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红石山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远看孟窑红一片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村里出现红石山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过路行人都来瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来是红枣堆成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（孟窑小学  李芳）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里万里红艳艳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小铁炉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千千万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走上山头看一看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里万里红艳艳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二堡小学三年级"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钱维珍）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万把斧头砸碎山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小斧头一斤半，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸起石头响连天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斧头虽小力量大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万把斧头砸碎山。（工农中学王世牡）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁敢来侵犯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人把铁炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼出钢铁山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁敢来侵犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扔到炉里边！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（小学五年级"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张振明）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷捋胡哈哈笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老爷爷，七十三，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慢慢走进幸福院。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一进大门往里看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪白的房屋照花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷捋胡哈哈笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝着北京把头点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（工农中学一年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"级胥润梅）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"休息还把书来念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小儿歌几千万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地里干活一大片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活儿干的快又好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"休息还把书来念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（泉子沟小学四年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"级卢长才）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电喇叭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电喇叭，哇哇哇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有嘴，会说话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听听北京好消息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们也学会了普通话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（扬窑小学四年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"级  陈富）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}